  "instructions": [
    "cut the yukon gold potatoes into 1/8 inch thick katsuramuki-cut slices.",
    "heat the coconut oil in a comal over medium heat.",
    "add the chopped rosemary and thyme to the comal and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the sliced potatoes to the comal and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "transfer the potatoes to a serving dish and top with chopped scallions and grated cheddar cheese.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!",
